# trusted_message_ids
# ===================
# One regex per line for tightly controlled Message-ID formats.  Do not trust a
# whole domain unless only trusted software can generate IDs there.
#
# FAQ sequence:
# ^<faq-[0-9]{1,10}@example\.invalid>$
#
# UUID-like locally generated IDs:
# ^<[a-f0-9]{8}-[a-f0-9]{4}-[a-f0-9]{4}-[a-f0-9]{4}-[a-f0-9]{12}@bot\.example>$
